When Cursor auto-generates a Git commit message for this repository (including the Source Control panel "Generate commit message" sparkle button), you MUST follow these rules:

- Language: Simplified Chinese (简体中文) only — subject and body must be in Chinese
- Format: `<type>(<scope>): <简短描述>`
- Types: feat, fix, refactor, chore, docs
- Optional body: use `-` bullet points for key changes, one per line
- Forbidden: English subject lines, vague messages like "update" / "fix bug", long explanations

Example:

```
fix(crawler): 修复 CentOS 7 下 Playwright 启动失败

- 自动回退到 glibc 2.17 兼容版 Chromium
- 仅在最近一次执行失败时展示失败原因
```
